TY  - JOUR
TI  - The Simplex Method for Quadratic Programming
AU  - Wolfe, Philip
AB  - [A computational procedure is given for finding the minimum of a quadratic function of variables subject to linear inequality constraints. The procedure is analogous to the Simplex Method for linear programming, being based on the Barankin-Dorfman procedure for this problem.]
C1  - Full publication date: Jul., 1959
DB  - JSTOR
DO  - 10.2307/1909468
EP  - 398
IS  - 3
PB  - [Wiley, Econometric Society]
