TY  - JOUR
TI  - Generalization of the Rank and Order Conditions for Identifiability
AU  - Fisher, Franklin M.
AB  - [The problem of the identifiability of a structural equation under nonlinear and nonhomogeneous restrictions on its parameters is examined. The usual results for the linear and homogeneous case are generalized and some consequences for the use of a priori inequalities are derived.]
C1  - Full publication date: Jul., 1959
